#

Carrot Salad with Raisins

10 min
$5
120 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Side Dish

Tags:

SaladHealthyQuickVegetarian

Description

A refreshing and sweet salad that combines crunchy carrots with plump raisins, perfect as a light side dish or snack.

Ingredients

  • carrots: 4 medium, grated
  • raisins: 1/2 cup
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • lemon juice: 1 tablespoon
  • honey: 1 tablespoon (optional)
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
